OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will see sunny
OL,6,Fspells and scattered showers,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy. This afternoon
OL,8,Fwill see bright spells with showers
OL,9,Fgradually dying out. Rain spreading to
OL,10,FGalloway towards evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will spread northeast
OL,13,Fduring this evening and in the early
OL,14,Fhours. Drier weather developing later
OL,15,Fin the night. Strong southwesterly
OL,16,Fwinds along the northern Argyll coast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FRemaining changeable and
OL,19,Foften cloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,20,Fheavy at times. A mild spell of
OL,21,Fweather.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
